  "title": "Sales Engineer (Marine Engineering) #70837",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesale of Marine Equipment and Accessories</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Engineer (Marine Engineering)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas West Road (8 minutes walking distance from the MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: Monday – Friday, 9AM – 5:30PM (One Saturday per month, 9AM – 12PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3,800 + Variable Bonus + Medical Benefits</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and deliver technical presentations to customers, explaining products and services clearly.</li><li>Coordinate with customers and the operations team to assess service job requirements.</li><li>Work with administrative staff to arrange engineer deployment.</li><li>Manage order securing, renewal processes, and oversee overseas delivery/logistics.</li><li>Collaborate with sales teams to understand customer needs and provide appropriate sales or technical support.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the department head.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/ Bachelor’s degree or higher in Marine Engineering or a relevant field.</li><li>At least 1 year of experience in the marine industry.</li><li>Strong technical knowledge of marine engines and spare parts.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills with the ability to build client relationships quickly.</li><li>Analytical and problem-solving mindset.</li><li>Mature, independent, and team-oriented with a positive work attitude.</li><li>Hands-on, proactive, and willing to take initiative.</li><li>Willingness to travel as required.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#70837 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
